This test models the cycle

  optparse-applicative has test-suite dependency on tasty 
  tasty depends on optparse-applicative

In the test, package "A" models optparse-applicative; there are two versions
available (1 and 2), and package "T" models tasty. 

The output of the test shows the versions of the packages involved, and it shows
that the direct dependency of optparse-applicative (A)'s test suite uses version
2, but the indirect dependency on itself (through tasty/T) uses version 1.

